divs: Sighting Details I was outside taking pictures of the clouds. I went around to the side of the house and was taking pictures of the chemtrails. I never even seen the object until I was checking my pictures on my digital camera. It is very hard to see the object without zooming in. This is the second time I have caught something on pictures I have taken within the past 2 years. I am putting the original photo on here as well as the one I just darkened a little so it is easier to see the object.
